title: High Pressure Jet Washer DJE-30
description: The DJE-30 is a sturdy high-pressure electric jet washer that is designed for professionals who require the highest quality of cleaning with no compromise. It can deliver the capacity of 150 bar of pressure and a hefty 15 liters per minute water flow This machine can cut through a tough mud, grease and industrial dirt easily and operates silently and quietly.It is ideal for both outdoor and indoor usage Ideal for outdoor and indoor use, the DJE-30 is powered by electricity, which makes it an energy-efficient, noise-free, zero-emissions solution suitable for homes, such as hospitals, schools warehouses, commercial buildings. With its sturdy construction, a easy-to-use design and consistently high pressure output the DJE-30 can be your ideal choice for reliable and sustainable cleaning.
keyFeatures: Up to 150 Bar High Pressure – Jet action is powerful enough to take on dirt, grime, and oil easily.
Electric Powered & Eco-Friendly – Clean and emission-free, ideal for those sensitive to noise and pollution.
15 L/min Water Flow Rate – Large surfaces are covered faster, reducing water consumption and time.
Low Noise Operation – Ideal for indoor or early morning use, without disturbing others.
Easy Maintenance – Simple controls, fewer moving parts, and reliable performance.
Ideal For – Industrial sites, car washing stations, warehouses, schools, hospitals, and many other noise- or emission-sensitive areas.
